RFC 5544: Binding Documents with Time-Stamps; Evidence object. 

 Evidence ::= CHOICE {
     tstEvidence    [0] TimeStampTokenEvidence,   -- see RFC 3161
     ersEvidence    [1] EvidenceRecord,           -- see RFC 4998
     otherEvidence  [2] OtherEvidence
 }
